Program: Free Thinking
Title: Narcissism: Will Storr, Olivia Sudjic, Tom Jackson and Sophie Scott
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b08t4gdw
Last Broadcast Date: Wed 14 Jun 2017
Shahidha Bari and Laurence Scott explore our obsession with the self. Take a look in the mirror with author and photographer Will Storr, the novelist, Olivia Sudjic, Tom Jackson, creator of Postcard from the Past and the neuroscientist, Sophie Scott. Producer: Zahid Warley Will Storr's book Selfie is published by Picador Olivia Sudjic's novel, Sympathy is published by One - the Pushkin Press imprint Tom Jackson's Postcard from the Past is published by Fourth Estate and @PastPostcard Sophie Scott is Professor of Cognitive Neuroscience at University College London. Show less